If Karim Benzema was among those who launched a football at the drone, he proved more accurate against Honduras.

This World Cup has so far seen the big-name forwards make an early impact and Benzema was no exception, the Real Madrid striker scoring twice on his World Cup debut.

‘He had a really good season with Real Madrid, winning the Champions League final,’ said Lloris.

‘That has given him good confidence. He played well during the preparation games and he was in excellent condition to play today.

